    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BodyRecords</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将人体摄影机的视角、阴森恐怖的边缘空间和身临其境的麦克风灵敏度独特地融合在一起--小心，你的声音可能会暴露你的身份。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在广阔、大气的环境中，玩家必须探索、解谜、躲避危险，同时收集重要信息以逃出生天。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《BodyRecords》中，团队合作至关重要。玩家必须密切合作才能解开谜题并取得进步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主要特点：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>车身摄像机透视: </strong>通过以动作为中心的体感摄像头视角体验身临其境的游戏。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/2fcad94b533758831ad74f3afcc436d0.poster.avif?t=1769062834\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/2fcad94b533758831ad74f3afcc436d0.webm?t=1769062834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/2fcad94b533758831ad74f3afcc436d0.mp4?t=1769062834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>麦克风灵敏度：</strong> 您的声音和音效会影响游戏，增加紧张感和沉浸感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/fd6489f73d36ba96ff367c0bca40bd8c.poster.avif?t=1769062834\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/fd6489f73d36ba96ff367c0bca40bd8c.webm?t=1769062834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/fd6489f73d36ba96ff367c0bca40bd8c.mp4?t=1769062834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>解谜：</strong> 深入直观而又引人入胜的谜题，丰富探索的内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/e700b4647e868dbfbcca121248d684f8.poster.avif?t=1769062834\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/e700b4647e868dbfbcca121248d684f8.webm?t=1769062834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/e700b4647e868dbfbcca121248d684f8.mp4?t=1769062834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>真正的合作游戏</strong>： 要想取得进步，就必须进行有意义的团队合作，因此协作对于生存至关重要。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >死亡并不是终结--当你死亡时，你会进入一个神秘的空间 “密室”（Backrooms），并有机会逃出生天，回到现实世界。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/d3191ef3939570e80a648aa30e2882f3.poster.avif?t=1769062834\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/d3191ef3939570e80a648aa30e2882f3.webm?t=1769062834\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3232040/extras/d3191ef3939570e80a648aa30e2882f3.mp4?t=1769062834\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索、解谜、逃生 - 携手揭开当地的神秘面纱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那么，您准备好捕捉您的旅程了吗？</p>",
